---
title: Creamy Pork Gnocchi with Zucchini
description: We've taken a classic Italian pasta dish and given it a seasonal twist! Fresh zucchini, basil and seared gnocchi in a creamy garlic sauce – because the best meals only require a few humble ingredients!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-pork-gnocchi-61bd56c1.jpg
